; Regression test for #735: ledger convert should produce a clear error
; when the CSV file has no date column, rather than crashing with an
; assertion failure.

test -f /dev/null convert test/regress/735-no-date.csv -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$sourcepath/test/regress/735-no-date.csv", line 1:
While parsing CSV line:
  $10,

Error: CSV line is missing a date field
end test
